n Probleme und behandelt neue Themen wie Fracking, seltene Erden sowie Novellen im Umweltrecht. Bergwerksbetriebe, Verwaltungen, Gerichte, Behörden, Hochschulinstitute und Industrie profitieren von diesem Werk.  aThe new edition of this standard work on the Federal Mining Act contains the most extensive presentation of and commentary on the complete mining law in force in Germany. The volume provides an overview of all problems related to mining law and addresses new topics like fracking, rare soils, and amendments to environmental law. Mine operators, administrations, courts, authorities, university institutes, and industry will benefit from this volume.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aMining lawzGermany. 4aBergrecht. 7aLAW / Public.2bisacsh  aMining law.1 aBoldt, Gerhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHammerstein, Fritz, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKappes, Christiane, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKeienburg, Bettina, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKühne, Gunther, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWeller, Herbert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWiesendahl, Stefan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2023z9783111318226oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97831107093910 cprintz978311070920940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311070928540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110709285423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.co